title: Cozy and Comfortable Spacious 1 Bed 1 Bath
posting_body: Conveniently located near shopping, pharmacy, and food centers, schools, a main bus line, and a trail head, we are tucked back in a park like setting.
We are a community of friendly and inclusive people.
Enjoy such features as a residents' lounge, fitness center, swimming pool, spa, playground and sports court.
We include a full size washer and dryer in every unit.
Let us pay your water, sewer, garbage, and basic cable for you.
Our on-site management and maintenance will meet your needs in a friendly and efficient manner.
Call Lacey Park Apartments to help you make us your new home today.
Storage units are available for $65 - $75 per month.
Carports are available for $25 per month.
Garages are available for $125 per month.
